---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy Policy for MortgageDash."
>
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pt-16 pb-24">
    <div class="card p-8 sm:p-12">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-8" style="color: var(--text-primary);">Privacy Policy</h1>
      
      <div class="space-y-6" style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7;">
        <p>Last updated: June 19, 2026</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4" style="color: var(--text-primary);">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>MortgageDash is a client-side calculator. We do <strong>not</strong> collect, store, or transmit any of the personal financial data you enter into our calculators (e.g., home price, income, down payment). All calculations are performed locally in your web browser.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4" style="color: var(--text-primary);">2. How We Use Information</h2>
        <p>Because we do not collect your financial data, we do not use it for any purpose. We may use anonymous, aggregated analytics (such as page views or state calculator usage) to improve our website's performance and user experience.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4" style="color: var(--text-primary);">3. Cookies and Local Storage</h2>
        <p>We use local storage strictly to remember your UI preferences, such as your choice between Dark Mode and Light Mode. We do not use cookies for tracking or advertising purposes.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4" style="color: var(--text-primary);">4. Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>Our website may contain links to third-party websites or state tax resources. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of these external sites.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4" style="color: var(--text-primary);">5. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4" style="color: var(--text-primary);">6. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please visit our <a href="/contact" class="text-[#06b6d4] hover:underline">Contact page</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
